Package todomato

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddProcessor
    This class contains methods to process add commands by the user.
    Command
    This class stores the different components of a user's command: the action, and the argument.
    CurrentDate
    This class stores the current date.
    Date
    This class stores the day, month and year of a date.
    DeleteProcessor
    This class contains methods to process delete commands by the user.
    DisplayProcessor
    This class contains methods to process display commands by the user.
    FileHandler
    This class reads, writes, and updates a local data file stored on the user's computer.
    Notification
    This class creates a pop up notification to appear on the desktop.
    Processor
    This class stores information needed to process a user's command, and contains methods to parse a command's arguments.
    SplitProcessorsHandler
    This class handles user commands by calling the processing method depending on the action specified.
    Task
    This class stores a Task description, and optional additional attributes.
    TaskList
    This class stores a list of all Tasks that the user wants to keep track of.
    Time
    This class stores the hour and minutes of a time.
    Todomato
    This class is the driver for the Todomato application.
    TodomatoFrame
    This class is the JFrame for the GUI of the application.
    UndoProcessor
    This class contains methods to process undo commands by the user.
    UpdateProcessor
    This class contains methods to process update commands by the user.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidInputException
    This class signals that the user has entered an unknown input.
